text: Pheux xallxhˌ ca di thrng lngthosʹ kæ phwk mu na fiki n chay læa phwk mu na fiki n hying læa brrda phu tang phakhi chay (mu chrikin) læa brrda phu tang phakhi hying (mu chrikat) læa pheux xallxhˌ ca thrng xphaythosʹ kæ brrda phu sraththa chay læa brrda phu sraththa hying læa xallxhˌ pen phuthrng xphay phuthrng metta semx
